Package org.apache.cactus.maven2.mojos

Class Summary
CactifyEarMojo A maven2 mojo that injects elements necessary to run Cactus tests into an existing EAR file.
CactifyWarMojo A maven2 mojo that injects elements necessary to run Cactus tests into an existing WAR file.
Dependency Dependency that we use for the lib folder add-on's.
EjbRef We extend the org.codehaus.cargo.module.ejb.EjbDef so that we can define custom ejbRefs in our pom.xml.
FilterRedirector We extend the FilterRedirector so that we can define custom redirector definitions in the pom.xml.
JspRedirector We extend the JspRedirector so that we can define custom redirector definitions in the pom.xml.
ServletRedirector We extend the ServletRedirector so that we can define custom redirector definitions in the pom.xml.
